[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "beginner"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/basic_major"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST has 20 points, a pretty strong hand to open 1\H. 

WEST has 12 points, and makes a Limit Raise, a jump to 3\H.

EAST is very, very close to bidding a slam. But she knows WEST has 12 points at most, so she should 
take the safe position and just bid 4\H.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "N"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "N:Q98742.KQ3.86.95 T.A864.KJ93.QT87 AJ653.JT9.AQ54.6 K.752.T72.AKJ432"]
[Declarer "S"]
[Contract "4S"]
[Result ""]
[Auction "N"]
pass pass 1S pass 4S pass pass pass
[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 3, chOption: S, chBasis: N, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:2, nBasis: 0, nRot: 2, useStandardVul: true"]
